          <h3 class="th03">연결되는 글</h3>
          <ul class="lc02">
                                                                                          <li class="l1">
                  <a href="/node/168" class="thumb"><span><img src="https://kyeol.kr/sites/default/files/styles/main_article/public/ATIS%20SWPA%20Research%20Report%20No.120_01.jpg?itok=orBDEga5" alt="연합군번역통역부(ATIS) 조사보고서 제120호"/></span></a>
